data.value:
Welcome to the Doc Odyssey Space travel game!
The year is 2121. Doc has taken the Delorean into the space age, but the car has taken some significant damage. Your mission is to purchase the correct supplies and parts to fix the Delorean and get back to Earth 1985 and prevent Marty-mageddon (Whatever that is...). Visit the planets to purchase the supplies you need to travel back in time!
